name: goldengoals.io NFT Football Marketplace
description:
goldengoals.io is the NFT marketplace dedicated to football, based on Tezos.

This is the Golden Goals logo, created using VQGAN+CLIP technology and rendered to high-res using ESRGAN.

Football is art, and Golden Goals is the football NFT Community

I am emilien.tez, founder of Golden Goals and I am glad to give this amazing community to football NFT fans. This community is yours.
